title: Noodles (Derivative) Project
body:
Doodle ID for Kudos: 1970

Discourse: https://forum.doodles.app/t/noodles-derivative-formal-proposal/402/

Rationale: The creation and launch of the Doodles derivative “Noodles” to promote our objectives: Embodying inclusivity, Funding the Doodlebank Treasury, Creating a Doodles Companion.

Timeline: In the case we meet minimum quorum and receive majority vote, definite project timeline will be determined upon receiving a Final Proposal from the Founders for any adjustments or changes required of “Noodles” project.
Current completion with current assets (estimates in %):
Art – 80%
Website – 85%
Smart Contract – 75%
Launch Plan – 30%
Community & Marketing – 10%
Rough projection of time required: (1-3 weeks)

Goal: Create our community of 6,000 Noodles, with 15-20% free mints (-gas) reserved for Doodlers. Raise 20% of initial mint revenue for Doodlebank. Set the precedent in which derivatives should be created and the manner that they are perceived in.

Cost: (+) Net Positive for Doodlebank

Accountability: Ethan is responsible for the organization of community, Justin is responsible for back-end and smart contract security, Fidel is responsible for front-end website development with integration for smart contract mint functionality. Revenue earned from the project will be secured and managed with a hardware wallet to secure the seed phrase. Payments to the Doodlebank will be hard coded in the smart contract to ensure the safety of funds.
